WEBVTT

00:08:28.722 --> 00:08:31.397
almost one woman out of every 100.

00:08:31.717 --> 00:08:36.550
Pneumonia took three children
out of every 10.

00:08:37.220 --> 00:08:39.333
More than anything else,

00:08:39.333 --> 00:08:43.708
we'd lose the confident way
we live our everyday lives.

00:08:44.836 --> 00:08:49.043
If you knew that any injury
could kill you,

00:08:49.043 --> 00:08:52.289
would you ride a motorcycle,

00:08:52.289 --> 00:08:55.500
bomb down a ski slope,

00:08:55.500 --> 00:08:58.976
climb a ladder to hang
your Christmas lights,

00:08:58.976 --> 00:09:02.643
let your kid slide into home plate?